snippet.title: Sailor Cats - Official Trailer 🐾
snippet.description:
♥ Play FREE: http://platonicgames.com/sailorcats.html

Sailor cats is the cutest fish-and-grow collecting game!

Help your lonely cat on its fishing adventure through becoming the most kawaii pirate in the world! Find friends to join its happy fleet, collect rare treasures and discover a-meow-zing new worlds full of crazy creatures and paw-some boats!

--

Game by Platonic Games: http://platonicgames.com/

Animation by the amazing team behind Sunshine Animation Studio: http://sunshineanimationstudio.com/

Music & SFX by David de la Peña

--

💙 Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlatonicGames
💜 Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PlatonicGames
❤️ Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/platonicgames_

Kawaii desu ne ~~  MEOW!! ﾐ(o*･ω･)ﾉ
